            strive to make the UI/UX as good an experience as I can.
          </p>
          <p>
            That's basically me. Read more about my education, experiences and
            skills below ‚¨áÔ∏è
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p class="mb-4 sm:mb-8">
            I've completed two Bachelor programs in the following fields. You
            can click them for more information:
          </p>
          {degrees.map((degree) => <DegreeCard degree={degree} />)}
          <p class="mt-8 md:mt-4">
            I'm also a qualified E.M.T. which is a skill I picked up in 2022 and
            briefly worked as in 2023.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Experience</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p class="mb-6 md:mb-8">
            While I've worked mostly in the IT field, I've been absent from my
            computer from 2021 to 2023 working very different jobs or travelling
            to see what else is there.
          </p>
          <ol class="relative border-s border-[var(--gray-700)] w-11/12 m-auto">
            {
              experiences.map((experience) => (
                <ExperienceEntry experience={experience} />
              ))
            }
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>(Work in Progress)</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <ContactCTA />
  </div>

  <style>
    .about {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3.5rem;
    }

    img {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    section {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      color: var(--gray-200);
    }

    .section-title {
      grid-column-start: 1;
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      color: var(--gray-0);
      text-transform: capitalize;
    }

    .content {
      grid-column: 2 / 4;
    }

    .content :global(a) {
      text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
      text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
      transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
    }

    .content :global(a:hover),
    .content :global(a:focus) {
      text-decoration-color: currentColor;
    }

    @media (min-width: 50em) {
      .about {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
      }

      .about > :global(:first-child) {
        grid-column-start: 2;
      }

      section {
        display: contents;
        font-size: var(--text-lg);
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
